1
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:54,660
Don't you understand?

2
00:00:54,660 --> 00:00:56,000
This is all a trap.

3
00:00:56,410 --> 00:00:58,160
The emperor teamed up with me long ago.

4
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,830
He covets your Bronze Soul Lamp,

5
00:00:59,830 --> 00:01:02,000
hoping to use its power for immortality.

6
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,000
And I just

7
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,000
used his hands

8
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:06,790
to force you to retrieve the memories you sealed yourself,

9
00:01:06,790 --> 00:01:08,539
to force you to remember who you are,

10
00:01:08,539 --> 00:01:10,539
to remember everything between us.

11
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:14,750
What is our relationship?

12
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:16,160
Who am I exactly?

13
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:19,220
Why do I reincarnate again and again,

14
00:01:19,910 --> 00:01:21,710
forgetting the past every time?

15
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:25,160
Why did you say I abandoned you?

16
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,080
You are A'Deng,

17
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:29,410
the ancient God of Creation,

18
00:01:29,410 --> 00:01:31,660
the world-saving soul formed from your own spirit,

19
00:01:31,660 --> 00:01:35,250
the lamp itself. And I am Shadow,

20
00:01:35,370 --> 00:01:36,660
your shadow,

21
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:40,039
the other half of your soul that was forcibly torn away.

22
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:44,000
A thousand years ago, the God of Creation split us in two.

23
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,289
You held the lamp fire

24
00:01:45,289 --> 00:01:46,830
and were revered by the world,

25
00:01:46,830 --> 00:01:49,789
while treating me as an evil spirit bringing chaos to the world,

26
00:01:49,789 --> 00:01:52,500
sealing me in the sunless abyss

27
00:01:53,250 --> 00:01:54,830
for a whole thousand years.

28
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:13,790
A'Deng saves the world

29
00:02:14,370 --> 00:02:16,170
and protects the common people.

30
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,100
She controls resentment

31
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:22,160
and suppresses evil spirits.

32
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:23,950
The two share the same origin

33
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:25,329
and cannot be separated.

34
00:02:25,329 --> 00:02:26,829
But my dear sister,

35
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:29,700
in the catastrophe 300 years ago,

36
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:35,000
you gave everything to protect him and this world.

37
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:38,540
In the end, I held you as you took your last breath.

38
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:48,410
I guarded your remnant soul through lifetime after lifetime.

39
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:51,329
But you never remembered me,

40
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:54,500
never thought of our past affection.

41
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,750
In your eyes, there is only him,

42
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:58,750
only this world that has failed you.

43
00:03:10,370 --> 00:03:11,910
No, no.

44
00:03:23,540 --> 00:03:25,500
I am the general defending this city.

45
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:27,100
May I ask for the lady's name?

46
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:30,500
My name is A'Deng,

47
00:03:31,540 --> 00:03:34,790
a lamp that warms people with stardust.

48
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:50,320
I promise you lifetime after lifetime,

49
00:03:50,370 --> 00:03:51,500
year after year.

50
00:03:52,329 --> 00:03:53,260
Year after year.

51
00:04:19,450 --> 00:04:20,750
If there is a next life,

52
00:04:22,410 --> 00:04:24,330
I will protect you completely.

53
00:04:24,910 --> 00:04:25,700
A'Deng,

54
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:27,870
see you in the next life.

55
00:04:36,580 --> 00:04:38,290
Lifetime after lifetime,

56
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,260
we will not be separated by life or death.

57
00:05:29,410 --> 00:05:30,200
Jingchen.

58
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,790
A'Deng,

59
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:06,910
I'm here to marry you.

60
00:06:08,330 --> 00:06:11,000
On the day Xie Jingchen came first in the imperial examination,

61
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,580
he suddenly fell ill

62
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:14,380
and coughed blood incessantly.

63
00:06:19,330 --> 00:06:20,120
A'Deng,

64
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:22,550
when I pass the examination,

65
00:06:23,330 --> 00:06:25,450
I will definitely give you a grand wedding

66
00:06:25,450 --> 00:06:26,450
and marry you.

67
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:33,080
If the lamp burns for a day,

68
00:06:33,370 --> 00:06:34,970
I will wait for you for a year.

69
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,790
A'Deng,

70
00:06:41,620 --> 00:06:42,950
see you in the next life.

71
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,909
Jingchen.

72
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:53,440
With heaven and earth as the hall,

73
00:06:54,659 --> 00:06:56,720
and mountains and rivers as witness,

74
00:06:58,159 --> 00:07:00,160
I wish to stay with you all my life,

75
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,650
until our hair turns white.

76
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:13,370
Wait for me.

77
00:07:14,410 --> 00:07:17,470
Passing the Chang Gate again, everything has changed;

78
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:21,450
why did we come together but not return together?

79
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:25,300
The phoenix dies after the frost falls on the parasol tree;

80
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:29,870
the white-headed mandarin duck flies alone without its mate.
